name: "Oregon" Elite Socks
description:
DUE TO HIGH ORDER VOLUME, ORDERS WILL BE DELAYED BUT THEY WILL STILL ARRIVE 1-3 DAYS BEFORE CHRISTMAS. ENJOY!!

The first release in our college series. Win the day!


You will not find these custom Nike elite crew socks in stores ANYWHERE.

Got a team order? Got a question? Shoot us an email and we will respond!

Features 
The Nike Elite Basketball Crew Sock features a midfoot compression fit for a secure, stable design that helps keep socks and cushioning in place. Dri-FIT® fabric wicks away moisture to keep feet dry and cool. Footstrike cushioning. Clearly defined pattern is more closely aligned to pressure patterns on the feet. Anatomical left and right provides superior fit and cushioning. Sold as single pair. 62% polyester/21% nylon/15% cotton/2% spandex. Imported. 
• Dri-fit fabric that pulls away sweat to help keep you cool and comfortable 
• Reinforced heel and toe for enhanced durability 
• Left/Right specific design for a better fit 
• Supportive fit with arch compression 
• Stripes up the back!

NOTE: These are AUTHENTIC Custom Nike Elite Basketball Crew Socks, with colors suggested by elite basketball players. All packaging is original. Please notify Nike Inc. if you know of any stores that sell counterfeit goods. Crew Fit Nike Elite Sock embellished in an All Over Print. Please note each sock ordered will be different as no two socks are alike due to our process to create the sock. This means that no one will be sporting the same sock as you! Guaranteed. Not affiliated with Oregon.
